{"tid":531400,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"內地近幾年既古裝劇真係好鍾意以南北朝做背景","createTime":"2018-01-16T18:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T04:43:00.000Z","uid":36134,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8ae980f81e988cc789b9ff8fc962fd5be3358b34","tid":531400,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T18:52:22.000Z","msg":"陸精 楚喬 瑯邪榜  蘭綾王<br />\n好多數都數唔晒 <br />\n好多劇 一聽慕容啊 拓拔 宇文<br />\n就知咩料 <br />\n再唔係就參考南北朝整個架空歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但內容真係好低汁 全部係d偶像派黎演<br />\n情情塔塔佔左大半部分<br />\n我大部分只係睇過一兩集 <br />\n瑯邪榜好似好少少（我無睇 朋友推介）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舊年真正高汁古裝劇既得兩套<br />\n射雕同司馬懿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7484172d9a7bb9b7c0c89aa93cf3fab2e07340ac","tid":531400,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T18:52:53.000Z","msg":"射鵰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ed3247a88152ee71f75ad41e3b2f974a61a960","tid":531400,"uid":161407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T18:57:28.000Z","msg":"17年都淨係睇呢兩套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e367f56ef5926b976d901ddf5d7182584a6168","tid":531400,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T18:58:17.000Z","msg":"慕容 拓拔 宇文<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59eae245af358b6253e1f005547c93ada2203db","tid":531400,"uid":41629,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T19:00:46.000Z","msg":"睇過琅琊同蘭陵<br />\n兩套都冇咩特別<br />\n步步驚心同甄嬛傳仲好過佢地"},{"pid":"61651592f3465574a39bc09b44060ceaa762666a","tid":531400,"uid":64884,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T19:01:10.000Z","msg":"好睇唔睇睇大陸劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f91a3ee690969434b6dc5abc61f0baa013c25ff","tid":531400,"uid":555,"like"